::Prowl::

Prowl frowns, taking the map from Klant. He couldn't believe these bots were leaving like that.

"I see.... So instead of trying to make the Maximals better, you're just walking off?" With the fuze he'd made with IR, he'd gotten a bit of her temper and was feeling a bit mad at these two, though it didn't show too much. "We finally have a very good base, the Maximals are training, and you guys are complaining about the past and leaving?"
